<promed@promedmail.org>
[This new fatal case of avian influenza virus infection, the 2nd in
the eastern Anhui Province, brings the total number of human cases in
China to 3 and the number of fatalities to 2. This 2nd fatal case in
Anhui province has yet to be confirmed independently by a
WHO-designated laboratory. Further information would be appreciated
concerning the nature of the "homemade" human avian influenza
vaccine; presumably a hen's egg-propagated inactivated preparation? -
Mod.CP]
